01:09:44.100 --> 01:09:46.330
Perfecting incentives which will work

01:09:46.330 --> 01:09:48.150
even in the case of self interests.

01:09:48.150 --> 01:09:53.150
But, these will fail if they
compromise moral commitments

01:09:53.310 --> 01:09:55.910
that are necessary to
govern a modern society

01:09:55.910 --> 01:09:57.660
in which incomplete contracts

01:09:57.660 --> 01:10:00.573
is just a very dangerous kind of utopia.

01:10:01.920 --> 01:10:06.010
Now, securing a
sustainable and just future

01:10:06.010 --> 01:10:09.930
will require that we take
seriously, as Aristotle did,

01:10:09.930 --> 01:10:11.670
the kinds of moral development

01:10:11.670 --> 01:10:13.960
that we're engaging in our society.

01:10:13.960 --> 01:10:16.210
