01:14:42.930 --> 01:14:45.720
the were the two richest guys in town.

01:14:45.720 --> 01:14:48.070
The two rich guys in the group,

01:14:48.070 --> 01:14:50.410
obviously a huge imbalance,

01:14:50.410 --> 01:14:52.440
and they, the two rich guys,

