01:19:55.130 --> 01:19:56.530
What people care is,

01:19:56.530 --> 01:20:00.470
they care about their own
standing in the community.

01:20:00.470 --> 01:20:04.030
But when you said, how important is it

01:20:04.030 --> 01:20:05.093
