01:20:06.090 --> 01:20:07.820
Distinguish please with me between

01:20:07.820 --> 01:20:09.260
the two following concepts.

01:20:09.260 --> 01:20:11.653
One is guilt and the other is shame.

01:20:12.810 --> 01:20:14.690
Guilt is something that
you feel privately.

01:20:14.690 --> 01:20:16.810
Even if nobody knows about it.

01:20:16.810 --> 01:20:19.000
Shame is what you feel as
if you've done something

01:20:19.000 --> 01:20:20.760
about which you feel guilty

01:20:20.760 --> 01:20:23.110
and it's publicly recognized.

01:20:23.110 --> 01:20:25.920
Now, I think it's useful
to have those distinctions

01:20:25.920 --> 01:20:29.270
because both are at work.

01:20:29.270 --> 01:20:34.270
And when I do something good,
I do something generous,

01:20:35.620 --> 01:20:37.400
most economist would say,

01:20:37.400 --> 01:20:39.910
well you probably did that
because you're signaling

01:20:39.910 --> 01:20:42.560
to others your generosity
and that will improve

01:20:42.560 --> 01:20:45.260
the kind of trades that you
can engage in in the future.

01:20:45.260 --> 01:20:46.760
Which of course could be true.

01:20:48.070 --> 01:20:50.160
But, there's a concept in psychology

01:20:50.160 --> 01:20:51.910
called the looking glass self.

01:20:51.910 --> 01:20:53.690
You're looking in the looking glass.

01:20:53.690 --> 01:20:57.200
A lot of our signaling we do
to ourselves for ourselves.

01:20:57.200 --> 01:20:58.610
And here's why.

01:20:58.610 --> 01:21:01.640
We're never sure about
our goodness, our bravery,

01:21:01.640 --> 01:21:03.320
our kindness, or whatever it is.

01:21:03.320 --> 01:21:05.700
And we occasionally engage in activities

01:21:05.700 --> 01:21:09.570
to reassure ourselves to
daily reproduce ourselves.

01:21:09.570 --> 01:21:11.920
Reconstitute ourselves.

01:21:11.920 --> 01:21:15.200
So that kind of self signaling
is something which goes on

01:21:15.200 --> 01:21:18.480
even in the absence of
others observing you.

01:21:18.480 --> 01:21:20.740
Now, how important is one and
how important is the other

01:21:20.740 --> 01:21:22.883
surely depends on the context and so on.

01:21:23.720 --> 01:21:28.620
But, when people do things which are kind,

01:21:28.620 --> 01:21:31.580
brave and so on, entirely
with nobody looking

01:21:32.440 --> 01:21:34.540
it could have a part of
that looking glass self

01:21:34.540 --> 01:21:36.100
aspect of it.

01:21:36.100 --> 01:21:38.733
But, I think the last question is,

01:21:40.790 --> 01:21:43.140
your last question about
the role of the community,

01:21:43.140 --> 01:21:44.543
