01:23:17.020 --> 01:23:18.920
well I have some benefits of my action

01:23:18.920 --> 01:23:21.020
and I care about the benefits of yours.

01:23:21.020 --> 01:23:23.970
So I put some little extra
next to your benefits.

01:23:23.970 --> 01:23:26.330
Well, that's a lot of what generosity

01:23:26.330 --> 01:23:27.950
and being a good citizen is.

01:23:27.950 --> 01:23:31.040
But, a lot of it is not
that I'm doing something

01:23:31.040 --> 01:23:32.830
like I'm transferring something to you.

01:23:32.830 --> 01:23:35.410
I'm doing something because
it's the right thing to do.

01:23:35.410 --> 01:23:38.650
Deontologically, that
it's not consequentially.

01:23:38.650 --> 01:23:40.723
It's a fundamental aspect of Buddhism.

01:23:42.093 --> 01:23:43.970
And, I think a lot of, for example,

01:23:43.970 --> 01:23:45.960
a lot of the self signaling is actually

01:23:45.960 --> 01:23:48.150
reassure ourselves that we are good

01:23:48.150 --> 01:23:49.763
quite apart from who's looking.

01:23:50.650 --> 01:23:55.650
