a missing set of terms

01:23:56.330 --> 01:23:58.090
in the way, at least in economics,

01:23:58.090 --> 01:24:00.000
we think about these things because

01:24:00.000 --> 01:24:03.730
we're always, I mean, if get
away from Homo economicus

01:24:03.730 --> 01:24:05.440
then what the individual is

01:24:05.440 --> 01:24:08.710
is putting a weight on
someone else's wellbeing.

01:24:08.710 --> 01:24:11.720
