01:25:20.810 --> 01:25:23.530
- No, I can say something about that.

01:25:23.530 --> 01:25:25.320
For most of the time

01:25:25.320 --> 01:25:28.730
when biologically modern
humans have existed,

01:25:28.730 --> 01:25:31.420
we did not live in Buchanan's world.

01:25:31.420 --> 01:25:33.820
We lived in worlds in which we interacted

01:25:33.820 --> 01:25:35.830
with relatively small number of people.

01:25:35.830 --> 01:25:37.430
Not as small as most people think.

01:25:37.430 --> 01:25:39.760
I mean it could be
dozens or even hundreds.

01:25:39.760 --> 01:25:41.940
But, we interacted with a group of people

01:25:41.940 --> 01:25:44.710
in which there were no contracts,

01:25:44.710 --> 01:25:47.690
there was no state to enforce
the contracts if there were.

01:25:47.690 --> 01:25:51.200
