01:25:53.880 --> 01:25:55.730
the perfect contracting rule.

01:25:55.730 --> 01:25:59.100
Nor were there rules of private property

01:25:59.100 --> 01:26:01.670
applied to virtually all things of value.

01:26:01.670 --> 01:26:02.830
A few things were.

01:26:02.830 --> 01:26:05.750
So, I'm talking about hunter-gather life

01:26:05.750 --> 01:26:08.200
up until 11000 years ago.

01:26:08.200 --> 01:26:12.240
