4000 years of the Neolithic

01:26:12.240 --> 01:26:17.240
there was very little of what
matters was private property.

01:26:17.590 --> 01:26:19.360
For example, almost certainly not land.

01:26:19.360 --> 01:26:21.440
But probably stores.

01:26:21.440 --> 01:26:22.963
So the idea that we were,

01:26:23.970 --> 01:26:28.930
